    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of a subdivision of the Lakota Sioux who formerly inhabited an area from the Black Hills in South Dakota to the Platte River, currently residing primarily in west central South Dakota.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
